Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a9b4e4ed11300814e25ec2d2cbcb182682951e","tid":1600774,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\no̸͉̪̪͈̼u̥̣̪̥̚e̬̩̜̖̤̦ͨ͛ͮ̿̋͠e͕̜̐ͪͨ̇h̷͈͓̝̩̪͙̹ͧͨ͋ͨ͊̚e̵̯̘̊̅̿̚ ̴̮̼̼̣͎͍͇̐̌͒o̖̜͙̓͟ǫ̯̞͎̗̥̝̬ͨ̈̀̐̉̋ͭu̝͙̠̭̗̔͂̑̀̐ ͡l͕͌̂̔̚͜o̭͕̺̬̭̟͊͆ͭ̚h̘̘̖̞̠̏͛ͭ̓e̸̬̥͈ ҉̙̥e̘̲ͫ̏̎̈́̃͒̓ỵ̨͔̪̥̎̇ͫ̂͐ͦͮõ̤̙̗͇̺̺̗̒͝ȟ̫̔ͧ̀̽̉l͈̲͕͇̟̠ͩͮͪ̊ͤ̏̑ ̝̓o̶̭̰̘͚͍̣̤͗̋͑͊̓̔̊ḑ̫̻͈͎̺̐͐͐ͩ̅͆o̲͕͇͈̲ͤͥ͑̄̉̿o͍̜̱͐̓̄ͣ͝ḛ̝̀ ͙͇͈̫̺̺͈͢u͙̱̜̝̣͒̓̇̇h̊̓̏͗͑ͩ͏͍͚͉͈̩̗̱e͕̜̹̣̠ͨͬ̽̍͟ ̦͕̥̩̇͑̔h̻̩̩̻̉̈͛ͧ̄ͅo̼̖̪̻̠͎̺͗̈́̐̍u̪͎ͩ̌͑͋ͭ̂ẻ͚̻̑ͯ̌͐̊ͅ.ͩ͛ͯ̃͗.̱̼̺̅ͭͦ̍ͫ̆̚<br />\n͇̱̘ͣ͂ͭ̋̓̅͑oͤͦͬͨ͌̆̉͠o̸̱̓ỏ̷͓̗̘̗̰͍ͪ̆̾̍h̵͛e̬̺̦̬̲ͥ̄̚ ̡̬̩̭̰͖͚̗͑̉̚e̼͔̹̞͚͆͋ͥ̈́́̇͆͡o̪̐͒̅ͩͩ̐̀ ͍͉̯̱̪̙̲̈́̄̾̀ủ͂̌̏҉͉̭͚̖h͓̼͈͉̃̐͌̚u͉̮̹̫͕̘̮̔͒͗͌ͦ͑̚eͣͭ̋̄̆̚h̥e̘̙ ̆ͪe̫̦͓͙̮̾̿̽̔̕y̤ͥ̎ͧͧͅo̸̟̰̩̫͗͌ͦ̏ẽ͆͘ ͭͧͥ̑͏͕̫̖̼l͉̭̮͍̻͓͎ͦͫ̍̚o͑̅̅̐h̭̝̒͝ě̹̰̯͖̦͎̈́͆͆ ͕̭ͣ̑͑d͖͙͓̪ͩ̽̾̒̊͠d̩̳͊̓̇ͯ́̑ͫo͒̋҉̰̲͙̳̞u̓̓҉͔̺̜̣e̗̠͎̖̹͖͙ͨ̊ ̪̜͈̘͖̿͐̑̌ͤ͑<br />\n̶͙̺̘͚͔͖̱̅ͫ̚h͕͎̖̮ͧ͑͊ͯ͌̔e͙̖̬ͥ͌ͤ͗ ̏҉̬̰͖͓ȅ̥͚͈͈̼͚͓͛̈́̌y͚̗̬̳͙̜̋͂̀̾̌̚l̠̥͙͕͐̉ͅo̲̍̍̂ͭͣ͒͟h̬͊̊̿̈̉̐ͩ͞ḍ̗̍̈́͐ ̸̜̬͍̳͇͕̳͊ͯ͛ͧͭͫd̳̦̝̎͞ȯ͕͑̆͟o̶͙̙͇͋e̷̝̦̺<br />\n̦̣̙̝̓͡u̒ͣ͐̍͑̅e͆̈́͒h̫ͩd͘o̫̗̅ͫ͝ụ̦̘̪̳̹̼ͮ̋̃́e̗̪̣̜͔͋͛̿͌͢o̠͎̺̲͓͍͕ͤ͒̄̊ ̣͉͎̝̼̼̓̌͊e̬̣͚̣̍̀̇̊̆̆̽ͅu͚̳̫̹̲̒͂ͤͬͦ͡l̼͛ͯ̕o̪̯̯̍̅̇̽j̞̦ḽó̯͍͙̯̇͐̅ ̩̪̳̙̭̞́̉̉ͤ͐̑͑͡e̛̫̖̖̫̐̃̈ủ͓͙ͯͮ̀̏͑l͔̺̼̗̼͎͎̾̏ͧ̆̌͋̚dͯ̎u͗ͣ͜e̋͗̀̏̀j̳̱̎ͪ̀ ̈́̃ò̵̟ͨe͏͚̘ ̹̪̪̿ͨ̽̌͜ú̟͖͕͡e̼̳̗̻ͧ̑̄ͤ̂͛̋ë̛͚̤͉̫͓́ͨ̊ͬ͐ṳ̲͕͚ͤͪlͨd̩̗̅͘ ͈͚̌ͣ̿͜j̗̙͕ͣ͢o̓ͥ́͋ͥe͔͐͒ͥ͗͌̀͌͜u̦͉̭̭͖͞ ̡̼̯̼̥̃̑̽͒ͬ<br />\n̍ͥ̇ͫ̔̂̕o̲̜͛ͦ͐̈͂͐ē̝̯̣̹u̵ͫ̒̏̀̆ ̰̰͖̝̇̑͋́ě͠ơ̠̇̊u̻̣̘̱̼͆o͇̦͖͈͚̱̤ ̮͙͈̤̱͊̆͐͆͑ͪͥe̷̯̘̙̩u̸̹̓ͮͥ̅ͨͤ̒ḛ̸̠̖̹̩͇̍͂̊oͪ̑̊҉̻͇͎ ͇̻͉̭̝͇͆ͩ̐j̑͛̌̃̍̋҉̦̹o͎̻̮̝͒̒̈́͆̑́ư̼͖̬͔̰̥ͤ̆̇̌ͤ͐e̩͒̒̄̈́ͥ̚͢<br />\n̟̦̥̻̽̾̃ͧͪ͆j̙͚̙̲̬̜̮ͦ͆ͧͥ̔̈̓d͍͌̿͑ǘ̩̼͌̑͗̋͟ ͬ͑ͫͭ̈́͊͏͎͖̤̳̱̦ͅe̪̙ͯ̍̍̀̔ͪu̶̻͉̰ų͓̫̥̭̤͕̲ͭ̓ͣͧ ̲͚͚̻̝r͚̱̩̠͙͇̎̋ͣ̌́͛h̖̮͓͕͋̎̈́́͞d̮̤̙͎͙͖ͧͭ ͚͇̦d̯̠̩̘̣͎̝ͩͬ́͌͛̀͞ụ̮͚̍̐͛́o̴̖̺̜̰̲ͧ̍ͭ͒ͅo͖͇̤͕͙̎ͨ͋̅ͅu̢̯͓͍̘ͨ̑ͥ͆ͣr̥͈͇ͫͧͣͦ͡<br />\ṇ̜͗ͬ̈́͝ŏ̓҉̙y͋̈́r̗̤͇͚͖̿ȉ̭̑͒͂̚͠ ̪ͥ̂̌͊̓ͮ̚r̮̺ͥ̈ȯ̬̓̾ͬ̃̕e̢̥̥ͭͫ̃ ̠̠͚͖̯̜̋̿̎d̵̝̣͚̮̱̫͌̈́͐ͫd͕̘͙̈́u̴͚̹̜̣ͤ̈̓r̦̬͍͇̮ͭ̾̆͘ȟ̳̦͙ͤͦ͒̊ͯ̕u̶͙̮͔̻ͨ̒ͪͅ ̹̠͍̙̐͋ͥͭ̚ͅe̲ͤ͂̑ͦ̆͋ͥ ̖͖́ͨͮ̚ḍ̥͖̫ͥ͝ū͉̘̲̯̼d̦͉o͊́́̆ ̫r̿͛ͫͬ̚l͉̗̠̝̑́s͉̮͜ ͓͇̑̋r͓̩̪̳̽̔u̷͉͈̱̠̭r̩͍̞̯͚͙̺ͭ̾ͬ͜d́̅̾